432
00:37:15,670 --> 00:37:17,980
This color really suits you.

433
00:37:18,710 --> 00:37:19,320
Does it?

434
00:37:22,020 --> 00:37:23,220
I just didn't expect

435
00:37:23,990 --> 00:37:25,400
