438
00:37:37,540 --> 00:37:38,480
But today,

439
00:37:38,590 --> 00:37:39,880
I saw him at the government's

440
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:40,600
press conference.

441
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:42,840
